Package: replicateAGCApaper
Title: Replication Compendium for Anchored Geodesic Component Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alberto", "Quaini", email = "alberto91quaini@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Research compendium for reproducing the simulations and empirical
    analyses in Anchored Geodesic Analysis for Multivariate Extremes. This
    package is not intended for CRAN distribution;
    it stores raw data, transformed data, generated results, figures, and
    paper-specific scripts. The reusable methodology is implemented in the
    companion package AGCA4extremes.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    AGCA4extremes
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Remotes:
    local::../AGCA4extremes
Config/testthat/edition: 3
